<item>
            <title>[CASSANDRA-3445] recognize that &quot;SELECT first ... *&quot; isn&apos;t really &quot;SELECT *&quot;</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/CASSANDRA-3445</link>
                <project id="12310865" key="CASSANDRA">Apache Cassandra</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;QueryProcessor includes the row key in &quot;first *&quot; because it mistakenly thinks the full row is being requested.  &quot;first *&quot; should really be treated like a slice.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
